Egypt video & photo dump. We only had one day to explore this historical city. It was impressive to see the great pyramid in person. Like every other cities, we met both nice and sketchy people. However, It’s the most chaotic city we’ve been so far. Tip #1: learn to bargain. Tip #2: always bargain. #egypt #pyramid #museum

Dubai is such a cool city to visit. Everything’s so new, so big, so fancy. The desert excursion was a life time experience. Shot out to @ahmedateeq, our local connection for the food and activity recommendations.
